textBody:
Iduna can mean several things:
* One of several modern anglicizations of the name of the Norse goddess Iðunn
* A literature society co-founded by Guido von List called Iduna (literature society)
* Asteroid 176 Iduna named after the goddess
* The Iduna language of Papua New Guinea
* A genus of tree warblers
* The journal of the Geatish Society
* Iduna, Wisconsin, an unincorporated community, US
